							<div class="related-topics"><a href="/ct/keyword/redirect.html?keywordid=17003&site=women">Books</a><span class="seperator"></span><a href="/ct/keyword/redirect.html?keywordid=17086&site=women">Brother Lawrence</a><span class="seperator"></span><a href="/ct/keyword/redirect.html?keywordid=14396&site=women">Compassion</a><span class="seperator"></span><a href="/ct/keyword/redirect.html?keywordid=14527&site=women">Evangelism</a><span class="seperator"></span><a href="/ct/keyword/redirect.html?keywordid=14615&site=women">Global Church</a><span class="seperator"></span><a href="/ct/keyword/redirect.html?keywordid=15547&site=women">History</a><span class="seperator"></span><a href="/ct/keyword/redirect.html?keywordid=14916&site=women">Missions</a><span class="seperator"></span><a href="/ct/keyword/redirect.html?keywordid=16475&site=women">Poverty</a><span class="seperator"></span><a href="/ct/keyword/redirect.html?keywordid=15142&site=women">Refugees</a><span class="seperator"></span><a href="/ct/keyword/redirect.html?keywordid=15151&site=women">Spiritual Formation</a><span class="seperator"></span><a href="/ct/keyword/redirect.html?keywordid=17062&site=women">Women</a><span class="seperator"></span><a href="/ct/keyword/redirect.html?keywordid=17063&site=women">Women in Leadership</a></div></div><div class="section"><span class="topics headings-small u-left uppercase">Posted:</span><span class="related-topics"><a class="nav_item" href="/women/2019/november/">November 4</a>, 
