<span data-id="194" data-name="featured_articles" data-itemtype="channel" data-itemid="162"></span><div class="border-top-black u-cf four-block-container spacer-top-30"><h2 class="section-heading spacer-bottom-30">Read These Next</h2><ul class="l-grid spacer-bottom-10 section"><li class="l-three l-grid_item spacer-bottom-30"><div class="bg-flag uppercase">Related</div>
<div class="img-container"><a href="/women/2017/may/starving-myself-meant-losing-myself.html"><img class="img-container_item" src="https://www-images.christianitytoday.com/images/76762.jpg?w=220" srcset="https://www-images.christianitytoday.com/images/76762.jpg?w=440 2x" width="220" alt="Starving Myself Meant Losing Myself" title="Starving Myself Meant Losing Myself" /></a></div>
<div class="slug uppercase spacer-top-10"><a href="/women/opinion/">Opinion</a><span class="seprator"> | </span>Discipleship</div>
<a class="title title-3 js-editableItem" href="/women/2017/may/starving-myself-meant-losing-myself.html" alt="" title="" data-type="article" data-id="138504">Starving Myself Meant Losing Myself</a><span class="lock-image"><img width="10" height="12" src="/system/img/icon_lock.svg" alt="Subscriber access only" title="Subscriber access only" /></span><div class="deck spacer-top-5">For years, I looked at myself in mirrors only to see mirages.</div>
<div class="byline uppercase spacer-top-8">Halee Gray Scott</div>
</li><li class="l-three l-grid_item spacer-bottom-30"><div class="bg-flag uppercase">Trending</div>
